channel.description:
[center] [img]http://deltascape.net/images/deltascape.png[/img]
[url=https://deltascape.net/faq.php?faq=deltascape#faq_ds_2014_return_faq]DeltaScape 2014 Return[/url]
[url=https://deltascape.net/]Forums[/url] | [url=https://deltascape.net/register.php]Register an account[/url] | [url=http://deltascape.net/client/DeltaScape%20Client%20v5.1%20%28standalone%29.zip]Download client[/url] | [url=https://deltascape.net/faq.php?faq=client_download#faq_deltascape_windows_client_faq]Client FAQ[/url] | [url=https://deltascape.net/highscores/]Highscores[/url] [/center]
[i][b]Register an account to play![/b][/i]
Credits to [url=http://www.rune-server.org/members/misanthropy/]misanthropy[/url] and his team for the 498 client we're using, along with the cache in his release of [url=http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/downloads/570504-arios-498-release.html]Arios 498[/url].
[b][COLOR=RoyalBlue]Features[/COLOR][/b] [center]
[COLOR=#d8ccaf][b]Combat[/b][/COLOR] Clipped combat (like RS) Clipped projectiles Autocasting Special attacks Prayers Poisoning [COLOR=#468f4d][b]Skilling[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#564b3a][b]100% Agility[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#7b6709][b]100% Cooking[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#757b7c][b]100% Fishing[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#72420a][b]100% Crafting[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#247b09][b]100% Fletching[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#dd4f01][b]100% Firemaking[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#00a900][b]100% Herblore[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#a79a99][b]100% Farming[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#757b7c][b]100% Mining[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#555b5a][b]100% Smithing[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#1b0692][b]80% Modern magic, 100% Ancient magicks[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#9db9a7][b]100% Prayer[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#8b3709][b]100% Runecrafting[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=purple][b]80% Thieving[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#000000][b]80% Slayer[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#096c02][b]100% Woodcutting ( + bird nests)[/b][/COLOR] [COLOR=#475ff1][b]Quests[/b][/COLOR] Cook's Assistant Doric's Quest Rune Mysteries Sheep Shearer Druidic Ritual Priest in Peril Lost City [COLOR=#cb5150][b]Minigames[/b][/COLOR] Barrows Duel Arena Fight pits Full treasure trails (work in progress) Warriors Guild Stronghold of security [COLOR=#bba781][b]Miscellaneous[/b][/COLOR] Character design Makeover mage Hairdresser Thessalia makeover Skill requirement menus Entity (NPC & Player) following (Double) Doors / gates Wilderness obelisks Teleportation items Amulet of glory Ring of duelling Games necklace Skills necklace Combat bracelet 24/7 uptime Frequent updates Highscores Custom Slayer point rewards
[b]Find more features on the [url=https://deltascape.net/showthread.php?t=94252]DeltaScape official forums[/url]![/b] [/center] [b][COLOR=RoyalBlue]Media[/COLOR][/b] [center]
